Interface Summary
IBaseService Interface for BaseService class.

IContactService Interface for ContactService class.
IListService Interface for ListService class.
 

Class Summary
BaseService Super class for all services.
CampaignService Performs all actions pertaining to the Contacts Collection.
ContactService Performs all actions pertaining to the Contacts Collection.
ListService Performs all actions pertaining to the Lists Collection.
